rows.label: qev090203_MSG0001
rows.name: Great. More of those things crawlin' on our wreckage.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090203_MSG0002
rows.name:
What do you figure their kind
even makes of the ol' ship, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090203_SEL0011
rows.name:
Say that it is just a place for
them to hole up for the night.

rows.label: qev090203_SEL0021
rows.name: Wonder if they collect the wreckage as treasure.

rows.label: qev090203_MSG0003
rows.name: Yeah? Well, now it's eviction time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090203_MSG0004
rows.name:
You got some weird ideas, pard. Anyone ever tell you that?
'Cause they should.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090203_MSG0005
rows.name: All right. Let's get over there and make with the blastin'![ST:wait ]
